<% content_for :title, "How to Play — Turf Monster" %>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-8">
  <%= link_to "&larr; Help Center".html_safe, help_path, class: "text-secondary hover:text-primary text-sm font-medium transition" %>

  <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-heading mt-4 mb-2">How to Play</h1>

  <div class="card p-6 mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-heading font-bold text-lg mb-3">30-Second Summary</h2>
    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-body">
      <li><strong>Pick 5 team matchups</strong> from the available slate.</li>
      <li>Each matchup has a <strong>multiplier</strong> based on team ranking &mdash; lower-ranked teams have higher multipliers.</li>
      <li><strong>Hold to confirm</strong> your entry (entry fee is deducted from your balance).</li>
      <li>When games are played, your score = <strong>goals scored &times; multiplier</strong> for each pick.</li>
      <li><strong>Highest total score wins</strong> the prize pool.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div x-data="{ open: null }" class="space-y-3">
    <div class="card overflow-hidden">
      <button @click="open = open === 'picks' ? null : 'picks'" class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-4 text-left">
        <span class="text-heading font-bold">Picks</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary transition-transform" :class="open === 'picks' && 'rotate-180'" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div x-show="open === 'picks'" x-collapse class="px-4 pb-4 text-body">
        <p>Each contest shows a slate of team matchups. Tap a team to add it to your picks. You need exactly <strong>5 picks</strong> to enter.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">You can enter the same contest multiple times with different pick combinations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card overflow-hidden">
      <button @click="open = open === 'multipliers' ? null : 'multipliers'" class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-4 text-left">
        <span class="text-heading font-bold">Multipliers</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary transition-transform" :class="open === 'multipliers' && 'rotate-180'" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div x-show="open === 'multipliers'" x-collapse class="px-4 pb-4 text-body">
        <p>Every team gets a multiplier based on their world ranking. The formula: <code class="bg-surface-alt px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm">1.0 + 3.0 &times; ln(rank) / ln(N)</code></p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Rank 1</strong> (best team) &rarr; x1.0 multiplier</li>
          <li><strong>Middle ranks</strong> &rarr; x2.0&ndash;x3.0 multipliers</li>
          <li><strong>Rank N</strong> (lowest team) &rarr; x4.0 multiplier</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">Picking underdogs is riskier but scores much higher if they score goals.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card overflow-hidden">
      <button @click="open = open === 'scoring' ? null : 'scoring'" class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-4 text-left">
        <span class="text-heading font-bold">Scoring</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary transition-transform" :class="open === 'scoring' && 'rotate-180'" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div x-show="open === 'scoring'" x-collapse class="px-4 pb-4 text-body">
        <p>For each of your 5 picks:</p>
        <p class="my-2 text-heading font-mono font-bold text-center">Points = Goals Scored &times; Multiplier</p>
        <p>Your entry score is the sum of all 5 selection scores. Entries are ranked by total score, highest first. Ties receive the same rank.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card overflow-hidden">
      <button @click="open = open === 'payouts' ? null : 'payouts'" class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-4 text-left">
        <span class="text-heading font-bold">Payouts</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary transition-transform" :class="open === 'payouts' && 'rotate-180'" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div x-show="open === 'payouts'" x-collapse class="px-4 pb-4 text-body">
        <p>Prizes are paid out based on your final rank in the contest. The payout structure depends on the contest format:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Small contests</strong> (5 entries max): 1st place wins $40</li>
          <li><strong>Large contests</strong> (25 entries max): 1st&ndash;5th place win prizes</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">If players tie, the combined prizes for their spanned ranks are split evenly.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Payouts are distributed in <strong>USDC</strong> to your balance. You can withdraw to your wallet at any time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
